Subject: [PATCH] ui: sidebar workspace switcher — connect WorkspaceManager

Wires WorkspaceManager (src/workspaces/workspace_manager.cc) into the
sidebar WebUI panel. The workspace switcher appears at the top of the
sidebar and shows named, color-coded workspaces.

Integration:
  - WorkspaceObserver → sidebar Mojo pipe → React WorkspaceSwitcher
  - SwitchToWorkspace() called on sidebar tab-group click
  - Active workspace tint applied via --fnc-ws-tint CSS variable
    (bridge: css-variable-theme-bridge.patch)
  - Tab suspension on workspace switch via SuspendWorkspaceTabs()

Hooks into SessionRestoreImpl to restore workspace state on launch.

TODO: Stub. Full implementation in Phase 2.
      Tracked: fennec-browser/fennec#13

PILLAR: Calm UI
JOURNAL: none
